[
{ type: install
  message: <<EOM
OpenSIPS ${PKGVERSION} was installed.

Enable and start with:
  sysrc opensips_enable=YES
  service opensips start

Configure shared / private memory in rc.conf if needed:
  opensips_shmem_size="64"   # -m, megabytes
  opensips_pkmem_size="8"    # -M, megabytes
  opensips_user="opensips"
  opensips_group="opensips"
  opensips_config="/usr/local/etc/opensips/opensips.cfg"

Edit ${PREFIX}/etc/opensips/opensips.cfg (installed from the .sample).

Docs: https://opensips.org/Documentation/Manuals
Migration: https://www.opensips.org/Documentation/Migration

RTP/media: consider net/rtpengine or net/rtpproxy alongside this port.
EOM
}
]
